column5: looking for help with putting a price tag on this package as i cant find anything about this boat on google.  1998 sylvan 14 cfs 14ft aluminum 3 bench boat trailer with all new electrical 2003 yamaha 15hp 2 stroke with gas can  i figure the motor is worth $1500 alone?
Without seeing it, I'd say $2000-$2500, maybe $3000 on the highside. Again, without seeing it...
I'm with Dax. Is there a trailer with it? Any accessories?   S.
A good way to compare prices is go on to the Auto Trader (Boat Trader) website and browse around.

i didnt have any luck finding any of these online at kijiji or autotrader.  it has a trailer, battery, lights, minn kota transom mount, old eagle fish finder, and the motor. ill get a pic tomorrow.  thanks
Assuming everything is in good working condition, I think you should be able to get 3000$. Good luck with your sale.
